---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Privacy Policy | ArtemisKit"
  description="ArtemisKit privacy policy - how we collect, use, and protect your data."
>
  <div class="container py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-stone-50 mb-4">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="text-stone-400 mb-12">Last updated: January 2025</p>

      <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none space-y-8">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-100 mb-4">Introduction</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">
            ArtemisKit ("we", "our", or "us") is committed to protecting your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your information when you visit our website and use our services.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-100 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-stone-200 mb-3">Information You Provide</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-stone-300 space-y-2 mb-4">
            <li><strong>Waitlist Signups:</strong> Email address, company size (optional), and intended use case (optional)</li>
            <li><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Any information you provide when contacting us</li>
          </ul>

          <h3 class="text-xl font-medium text-stone-200 mb-3">Automatically Collected Information</h3>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-stone-300 space-y-2">
            <li><strong>Usage Data:</strong> Basic, anonymized usage statistics to help us improve our services</li>
            <li><strong>Referral Source:</strong> The website that referred you to us (if any)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-100 mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-stone-300 space-y-2">
            <li>To notify you about ArtemisKit Cloud and API availability</li>
            <li>To respond to your inquiries and provide support</li>
            <li>To improve our website and services</li>
            <li>To send occasional product updates (you can unsubscribe anytime)</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-100 mb-4">Data Storage & Security</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">
            Your data is stored securely using Supabase, which employs industry-standard encryption and security practices. We implement appropriate technical and organizational measures to protect your personal information against unauthorized access, alteration, disclosure, or destruction.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-100 mb-4">Data Sharing</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">
            We do not sell, trade, or rent your personal information to third parties. We may share information only in the following circumstances:
          </p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-stone-300 space-y-2 mt-4">
            <li>With service providers who assist in operating our website (e.g., Supabase for data storage, Vercel for hosting)</li>
            <li>If required by law or to protect our rights</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-100 mb-4">Your Rights</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mb-4">You have the right to:</p>
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-stone-300 space-y-2">
            <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction of inaccurate data</li>
            <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Withdraw consent for marketing communications</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed mt-4">
            To exercise these rights, contact us at <a href="mailto:privacy@artemiskit.dev" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300">privacy@artemiskit.dev</a>
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-100 mb-4">Cookies</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">
            We do not use cookies for tracking or advertising purposes.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-100 mb-4">Third-Party Links</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">
            Our website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices of these external sites. We encourage you to review their privacy policies.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-100 mb-4">Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of significant changes by posting the new policy on this page and updating the "Last updated" date.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-stone-100 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
          <p class="text-stone-300 leading-relaxed">
            If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at:
          </p>
          <p class="text-stone-300 mt-2">
            <a href="mailto:privacy@artemiskit.dev" class="text-primary-400 hover:text-primary-300">privacy@artemiskit.dev</a>
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-stone-800">
        <a href="/" class="text-stone-400 hover:text-stone-200 text-sm">‚Üê Back to home</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
